<body>
    <h1>AccessPointAI Application</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>An AI application (AccessPointAI) for user provisioning automate=
s the process of handling user requests and sending them to a provisioning =
system (SailPoint IdentityIQ). AccessPoint uses natural language processing=
 (NLP) to understand requests from employees through a conversational inter=
face, like a chatbot, and machine learning (ML) to process and automate the=
 necessary access management tasks. This eliminates manual IT work, reduces=
 errors, and speeds up the user onboarding or access update process.&nbsp;<=
/p>
<h2 id=3D"AccessPointAIApplication-AccessPointAI">AccessPointAI</h2>
<p>AccessPointAI is a customized off the self AI tool or a custom-homegrown=
 application, AI-powered user interface designed to streamline and automate=
 the process of user provisioning. It is built from the ground up/customize=
d to fit a Assecnsion's unique workflows, business logic, and security prot=
ocols. Its conversational interface uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) =
to handle user access requests and automatically communicate with a backend=
 provisioning application</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrappe=
r image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conflue=
nce-embedded-image image-left" alt=3D"image-20251027-005555.png" width=3D"4=
